SUMMARY:Temporary Detention: A Guide to the Forced Assembly Centers
DESCRIPTION:Please note: this event is off site at Epworth United Methodist Church. \n\n\n\nLearn about a recently completed multimedia project\, Temporary Detention: A Guide to the Forced “Assembly Centers.” This interactive website explores the history and legacy of the 16 temporary detention centers operated by the Western Civil Control Administration during World War II. These Euphemistically called “Assembly Centers” these hastily-built detention centers imprisoned approximately 92\,000 Americans of Japanese ancestry as the ten concentration camps were being built. \n\n\n\nLearn more about these often unknown centers with the website’s creators: Sharon Yamato\, New York photographer Stan Honda\, and Densho Content Director Brian Niiya. \n\n\n\nTemporary Detention: A Guide to the Forced Assembly CentersWith Sharon Yamato\, Stan Honda\, and Brian NiiyaSaturday\, March 14\, 2pmEpworth United Methodist Church1333 SE 28th Ave\, PortlandPlease RSVP below. \n\n\n\n\n                \n                        \n                            RSVP for Temporary Detention: A Guide to the Forced Assembly Centers\n                             \n                        \n                        Name(Required)\n                            \n                            \n                                                    \n                                                    First\n                                                \n                            \n                            \n                                                    \n                                                    Last\n                                                \n                            \n                        Email(Required)\n                            \n                        Including yourself\, how many people are you registering for?(Required)Your zip codeWould you like to be kept up-to-date with our upcoming programs and events? Yes\, please!
URL:https://jamo.org/event/temporary-detention/
LOCATION:Epworth United Methodist Church\, 1333 SE 28th Ave\, Portland\, OR\, 97214
CATEGORIES:Exhibitions
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://jamo.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/Single-Mens-Dormitory-small.jpg
